diff --git a/CHANGES.rst b/CHANGES.rst
index 8b2813a..77d7a88 100644
--- a/CHANGES.rst
+++ b/CHANGES.rst
@@ -1,16 +1,21 @@
 Changelog
 =========
 
 main
 ----
 
+* Fix stub generation for nested classes. Previously, nested classes could render
+  with invalid Python syntax like ``class Outer.Inner:``. Now they render correctly
+  with proper nesting and indentation. Added ``class_stubs`` parameter to ``ClassStub``
+  and updated ``render()`` to support nested class hierarchies.
+
 * Add ``RewriteMostSpecificCommonBase`` type rewriter to replace union of derived classes with common
   base class (not enabled by default.) Merge of #311, fixes #298. Thanks Christoph Hansknecht.
 
 * Drop support for Python 3.7 and 3.8.
 
 
 23.3.0
 ------
 
 * Add ``--pep_563`` flag to ``apply`` command. Thanks Sagar Badiyani.
